The Vanguard Group

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Vanguard Investments Australia Ltd)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

For anarchist political group, see Vanguard Group (anarchist).

The Vanguard Group, Inc.









Type

Privately held company


Industry
Investment management


Founded
May 1, 1975; 42 years ago (May 1, 1975)


Founder
John C. Bogle


Headquarters
Malvern, Pennsylvania



Key people

F. William McNabb III (Chairman)
Mortimer J. (Tim) Buckley (CEO as of January 2018)


Products
Mutual funds
Exchange-traded funds
Brokerage
