Vanguard Investments Australia Ltd. Key Developments

Vanguard Australia Appoints Johanna Platt as Chief Financial Officer
May 8 17
Vanguard Australia has appointed Johanna Platt as its chief financial officer. In her new role, Platt will take care of leading financial operations at both management and statutory levels at Vanguard Australia. Platt has replaced Daniel Shrimski. Currently, Platt serves at Iron Mountain ANZ as a CFO ANZ region. Previously, she also worked for Mondelez International, Cadbury plc., Mayne Pharma, Mayne Nickless, FedEx, Laura Ashley and Kemcor Australia.


